snippet.textDisplay: In case y’all are asking how covid got there, there are people who sneak into china to do business and come back late night when no one sees them or bribe the soldiers to let them pass through since the soldiers also know and are sure the merchants would come back and not defect. There are plenty North Korean defectors who have youtube channels some which have eng subtitles so you can watch them. They get news cuz they still contact their relatives and friends back home idc if you believe or not but they still do and they tell news thats relatively new to you and things u prob didn’t even think of
